>
[Gnaw](/Feats.aspx?ID=2427) <actions string="Three Actions" />
</title>

<traits>
<trait label="Ratfolk" url="/Traits.aspx?ID=234" />
</traits>

<column gap="tiny">

**Source** [Ancestry Guide](/Sources.aspx?ID=74) pg. 54 <sup>3.0</sup>

**Prerequisites**
[Vicious Incisors](/Feats.aspx?ID=1301)

</column>

---

With enough time and determination, you can chew through nearly anything. You deal double your jaws damage to an unattended, inanimate object.
